message:

title: 820-00138 Green led & orange, but nothing
message:
Probably dead CPU, because voltage spike on VCORE.

You should check power on sequence at least.
Do you get 3V3_SUS?
Post S5_PWRGD, PCH_DSWVRMEN, PM_DSW_PWRGD, PM_RSMRST_L, PM_PWRBTN_L, PM_BATLOW_L.
Also check all 4 RTC signals at PCH.
Trigger SMC_ONOFF_L and check for reaction (drop pulse) at PM_PWRBTN_L.

Be sure to use 85W Magsafe 2 charger...
